_sText:
Welcome To De_danger

de_danger is a small 5v5 map, I am familiar with making defuse maps csgo, aim and fy maps in counter strike source, but not defuse maps for CS:S
And here we are! this is my first defuse map for CS:S

Counter Terrorist - Defend The Bombsites to prevent the terrorists bombing them.

Terrorist - Plant the bomb on one of the bomb sites.

Bombsite A - Houses, some oranges and uh crates

Bombsite B - The Palace, and more oranges? why does the terrorist want to blow up the oranges???

De_danger... that name does not fit the theme of dust, But oh well

Made In Hammerplusplus
